{"tid":653272,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"DigitalFoundry頻道: Crysis 10 Years On","createTime":"2018-05-04T14:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T14:45:19.000Z","uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a21837b8b005045d54bc3344d9a4819b57ecb24","tid":653272,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"Crysis 10 Years On: Why It's Still Melting The Most Powerful Gaming PCs<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PcYA-H3qpTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPcYA-H3qpTI&d=znF%2FQio4JK0JxDHoy3xseE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=790c2e83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PcYA-H3qpTI</a><br />\n雖然英文屎唔清楚佢講咩，不過睇完都知道07年既遊戲，技術到今時今日依然唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed82ba03aa52d49279b83854573e93b2fcecc15","tid":653272,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"另外上網我睇到，原來Crytek同NVIDIA合作開發crysis既時候，已經用到Navier-Stokes演算法<br />\n<a href=\"https://blogs.nvidia.com.tw/2014/04/help-best-get-better/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.nvidia.com.tw%2F2014%2F04%2Fhelp-best-get-better%2F&d=znF%2FQio4JK0JxDHoy3xseE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e205b734\" target=\"_blank\">https://blogs.nvidia.com.tw/2014/04/help-best-get-better/</a><br />\nRege 旗下的大多數工程師幾乎隨時都在執行外派任務，跟開發人員一同工作。Navier-Stokes 就是在外派任務期間首次提出的。這個作法也運用在「末日之戰 (Crysis)」首部曲上，當時有六、七名 NVIDIA 工程師外駐於 Crytek 的法蘭克福辦公室好幾個月，協助該遊戲上市。<br />\n<br />\nNavier-Stokes equations<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.grc.nasa.gov/www/k-12/airplane/Images/nseqs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grc.nasa.gov%2Fwww%2Fk-12%2Fairplane%2FImages%2Fnseqs.gif&h=2305a63c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}